#All the main declension systems
PATTERNS
OpenClassRegularNounDeclCanBeBare
OpenClassRegularNounDeclCantBeBare
NounDeclIrregularU
NounDeclNamesFinalI
InfinitivalDecl
RegNounFinalVowelDeclension

#suffix-based declensions
NounDeclUtjunSuffix
NounDeclUmSuffix

#Full-declension patterns

NounDeclIrregPolyWithN
NounDeclIrregularTimeVan
NounDeclOldOch
NounDeclOldFamilyOAblaut


# Dative+oblique only patterns
NounDeclOldAnForm
NounDeclFamilyNkForm
NounDeclOldRandomOAblaut
NounDeclCountry

