##########################

PATTERN InfinitivalDecl
#For declined infinitivals, I assume they're not pluralized
#I don't add the reduction boundary as a safety precaution
#I make bare infinitival get analyezd as just a verb
#TO DO: I don't think they can take attributive, but I put them here just to be safe

#Singular caseless definite and attributive
InfinitivalDeclStem  NSg0 DeclUWithFixedDef
#GAGA GAGA!	#Plural possessive
#GAGA GAGA!	InfinitivalDeclStem   PluralPossessiveDeclension


PATTERN InfinitivalDeclStem
Infinitival
:Neg Infinitival Neg:





