#GAGA GAGA!	[երբ<prn>:երբ] ([<rel>:]|[<itg>:])   SubstZero NouNinflBoundary 


PATTERN NounTimeVanStemBaseNoOrYesU
NounTimeVan 
NounTimeVanBase
NounTimeVanU 
NounTimeVanUReducedBase 

NounTimeVanIrigunBase

PATTERN NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithIrigun
NounTimeVan
NounTimeVanReduced
NounTimeVanU 
NounTimeVanUReducedReduced 

NounTimeVanIrigunReduced

PATTERN NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithoutIrigun
NounTimeVan
NounTimeVanReduced
NounTimeVanU 
NounTimeVanUReducedReduced 

PATTERN NounTimeVanStemReducedYesU
NounTimeVanU  
NounTimeVanUReducedReduced  

PATTERN NounDeclIrregularTimeVan
#optional normal case
#ժամ takes the above and dative ու

# մահ ամիս
NounTimeVanStemBaseNoOrYesU NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 (Def|Poss)? 
# մահվա  ամսվա
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithIrigun NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseTimeVanDatGenSuffixVa  
# definite մահ-վա-ն մահ-վան-ս ամս-վա-ն ամս-վան-ս
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithIrigun  NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseTimeVanDatGenSuffixVan Poss
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithIrigun  NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseTimeVanDatGenSuffixVa Def  
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithIrigun  NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseTimeVanDatGenSuffixVan Def # Dir/LR
# մահու ամսու
NounTimeVanStemReducedYesU  NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseDefUDeclensionWithOvertcase # Dir/LR
# մահվան
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithIrigun  NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseTimeVanDatGenSuffixVan # Dir/LR

# մահվանից ամսվանից իրիկվանից
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithIrigun NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseTimeVanDatGenSuffixVan AblReg Poss?
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithIrigun NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseTimeVanDatGenSuffixVan AblReg Def? # Dir/LR
# ամսից
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithoutIrigun NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 AblReg (Def|Poss) # Dir/LR
# ամսով ամսում
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithoutIrigun NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 InsReg|LocReg Poss?
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithoutIrigun NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 InsReg|LocReg Def? # Dir/LR
# իրիկունով
NounTimeVanIrigunBase NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 InsReg|LocReg Poss?
NounTimeVanIrigunBase NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 InsReg|LocReg Def? # Dir/LR

# մահվամբ
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithIrigun NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseTimeVanInsVamp (Def|Poss)? # Dir/LR 
# մահվա-ս
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithIrigun  NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseTimeVanDatGenSuffixVa Poss # Dir/LR

# ամիսի ամսի, զատիկի զատկի
NounTimeVanStemBaseNoOrYesU NZero NouNinflBoundary  CaseDefIDeclensionWithOvertcase # Dir/LR
NounTimeVanStemBaseNoOrYesU NZero NouNinflBoundaryRed  CaseDefIDeclensionWithOvertcase # Dir/LR

#Plural
NounTimeVanStemBaseNoOrYesU NZero NouNinflBoundary RegNounPluralFormDeclension 


#Singular attributive
#The ուանէ form is preferably treated as attributive
NounTimeVanStemReducedNoOrYesUWithIrigun NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 AttributiveVan





#GAGA GAGA!	#For irregulars among the time words
#GAGA GAGA!	#For irregulars derived from adverbs like այսօր
#GAGA GAGA!	#Bare adverb
#GAGA GAGA!	NounTimeVanAdvStem
#GAGA GAGA!	#Without case, but with definite
#GAGA GAGA!	NounTimeVanAdvNominalizedStem NouNinflBoundary NSg0 (Def|Poss)
#GAGA GAGA!	#With case
#GAGA GAGA!	NounTimeVanAdvNominalizedStem NSg0 CaseTimeVan NouNinflBoundary (Def|Poss)? 
#GAGA GAGA!	NounTimeVanAdvNominalizedStem NSg0 CaseRegI (Def|Poss)?  # Dir/LR
#GAGA GAGA!	#with possible case-boundary m like շատոնցմէ
#GAGA GAGA!	NounTimeVanAdvNominalizedStem NSg0 CaseBoundaryM CaseRegObliqueWithoutGen (Def|Poss)?  # Dir/LR


#GAGA GAGA!	#Attributive
#GAGA GAGA!	NounTimeVanAdvNominalizedStem NSg0 AttributiveVan

#GAGA GAGA!	#Plural
#GAGA GAGA!	NounTimeVanAdvNominalizedStem RegPluralDeclension

#GAGA GAGA!	#For irregular հիմակուան from հիմա
#GAGA GAGA!	NounTimeVanHima AdvZero
#GAGA GAGA!	NounTimeVanHima [:կ] AdvZero SubstZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseTimeVan NouNinflBoundary (Def|Poss)? 

#GAGA GAGA!	#singular attributive
#GAGA GAGA!	NounTimeVanHima [:կ] AdvZero SubstZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 AttributiveVan


#GAGA GAGA!	#Plural possessive (separate line for instrumental)
#GAGA GAGA!	NounTimeVanHima [:կուան] AdvZero SubstZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0|NPlReg PluralPossessiveDeclension



