#regularized plural and reguarlized case մարդերի, մարդիկից
NounIrregMan NZero  NouNinflBoundary RegNounPluralFormDeclension  # Dir/LR
NounIrregMan NZero  NouNinflBoundary NPlIrregIk CaseDefIDeclension  # Dir/LR

