#GAGA GAGA!	NounIrregMan NZero	 NouNinflBoundary NPlIrregIk  PossPl CaseRegPostPluralPoss? Def|Poss
#GAGA GAGA!	NounIrregMan NZero  NouNinflBoundary  PlDatGenIrregularOts CaseBoundaryM? InsReg PossPl  Def|Poss

