NounIrregMan NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 AttributiveGenIDef  # Dir/LR
NounIrregMan NZero NouNinflBoundary  AttributiveKAnts 



#տիկին
#regular caseless  տիկին
NounIrregWomanBase NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 (Def|Poss)? 
#regular dative case and oblique տիկինի տիկինից
NounIrregWomanBase NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 CaseDefIDeclension  # Dir/LR
#irregular dative case տիկնոջ and oblique տիկնոջից
NounIrregWomanReducedSg NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 DatGenArchaicOch (Def|Poss)?
NounIrregWomanReducedSg NZero NouNinflBoundary NSg0 DatGenArchaicOch CaseRegIObliqueWithoutGenAndDefPoss

#regularized plural and reguarlized case տիկինների
NounIrregWomanBase NZero  NouNinflBoundary RegNounPluralFormDeclension # Dir/LR
