NounIrregWomanReducedPl NZero NouNinflBoundary [<pl><dat_gen>:անց]  CaseRegIObliqueWithoutGenAndDefPoss

# optional անոց
NounIrregWomanReducedPl NZero NouNinflBoundary [<dat_gen>:անոց]  (Def|Poss)?  # Dir/LR

# frozen կին forms
NounIrregWomanReducedPlGinGn  NZero NouNinflBoundary [<pl>:անիք] CaseDefIDeclension # Dir/LR
NounIrregWomanReducedPlGinGn  NZero NouNinflBoundary [<pl><dat_gen>:անց] CaseRegIObliqueWithoutGenAndDefPoss? # Dir/LR


#GAGA GAGA!	#regularized plural possessive տիկիննիս տիկիններնիս
